  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK901">
<l>maṉaiviḻaivār māṇpaya ṉeytār viṉaiviḻaivār </l>
<l> vēṇṭāp poruḷu matu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who lust after their wives will not attain the excellence of virtue and it is just this that is not desired by those who are bent on acquiring wealth.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
